            <forecast-period index="1" start-time-local="2026-05-10T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-05-11T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-05-09T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-05-10T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Cloudy. Medium chance of showers in the morning and afternoon. Light winds becoming southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h in the early afternoon then becoming light in the evening. Overnight temperatures falling to around 11 with daytime temperatures reaching around 19.</text>
